---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions"
  description="Terms and Conditions for expensy — Money Leak Detector. Understand the terms of using our free personal finance analysis tool."
  canonical="https://expensy.com/terms/"
>
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-1.5">
      <span class="font-visueltpro text-xs tracking-wide text-mist-gray">Legal</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-bradford text-4xl font-medium leading-tight tracking-tight text-cloud-whisper sm:text-5xl">
      Terms & Conditions
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-2 font-visueltpro text-sm text-ash-accent">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <hr class="my-10 border-white/10" />

    <h2 class="font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      By accessing or using expensy.com (the "Website") and the Money Leak Detector tool (the "Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Service Description</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      expensy provides a free personal finance analysis tool that helps users understand their spending patterns. The Service processes user-entered financial data entirely within the browser to generate personalized spending insights, savings estimates, and financial health scores.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">No Financial Advice</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      The insights, recommendations, scores, and analysis provided by the Service are for informational and educational purposes only. They do not constitute financial, investment, legal, or professional advice. You should consult a qualified financial professional before making any financial decisions. Use of the Service is at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">No Data Storage</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      All data you enter into the Service is processed client-side in your browser. We do not collect, store, or transmit your financial information. Once you leave or refresh the page, your data is permanently lost.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      All content, design, code, and functionality on this Website, including the Money Leak Detector tool, are the property of expensy and are protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our express written permission.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      expensy, its operators, and affiliates shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Service. The Service is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, either express or implied.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting on this page. Your continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 font-bradford text-2xl font-medium text-cloud-whisper">Contact</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 font-visueltpro leading-relaxed text-mist-gray">
      For questions about these Terms, please <a href="/contact" class="text-cloud-whisper underline underline-offset-2 decoration-white/20 hover:decoration-white/60">contact us</a>.
    </p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
